'''The Great Pug''' is a PC-only bar [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|world]] established on February 1, 2017 by ''owlboy'', dedicated to host many patrons and serve all those who come through its doors.

==Layout==

The Great Pug has four floors:

* The first floor hosts a double-sided bar, 11 booths and 5 tables for patrons to sit, as well as two bathrooms, a storage closet, and a door leading out to the back of the building where dumpsters and a shed can be found
* The second floor, named "Night View Hall" has another bar, a stage for people to perform, a billiards table, two long tables and five small tables
* The topmost floor, named "The Roost", can be reached after ascending 6 flights of stairs. The Roost has a fireplace with four seats and a sofa surrounding it, two large round tables behind it, and another set of stairs leading to a loft with 5 beds for people to sleep on

