==Trivia==
[[File:Great Dane Pub ^ Brewing Company Eastside - panoramio.jpg|thumb|A photograph taken of the exterior of "''The Great Dane''" bar's 'East' location]]

* The Great Pug is based on the first floor of a real bar called "''The Great Dane''", located in [[wikipedia:Madison,_Wisconsin|Madison, Wisconsin]], USA. The Great Pug is inspired off of its 'East' location.
* The Great Pug has a quest-compatible sister world called '[https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_1917b43c-7d1b-4734-87db-2956c2069059 The Great Pug - West]', uploaded in 2019
* Footage of The Great Pug can be found in VRChat's [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PWLPw4RE9Ig 'Create, Play, Share' trailer].
* The music accompanying The Great Pug is [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oOcv_vDdRAA 'Together With You', by JD Tundra].
* At one point in time, inside one of the bathroom stalls had a phone number to call. If you dialed the number, an automated recording would play; the caller would be "put on hold", as The Great Pug's music would play while you waited. The line hung up after a while.

